Package client.model.map

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ICatanMap
    The datastructure that represent the Map in a Catan Game Domain: hexes, ports, roads, settlements, cities, robber, radius.
    ICommunity
    Interface for both cities and settlements
    IEdgeValue
    Represents the values used where a road is placed Domain: a player and edge location
    IHex
    Represents a Hex in the Catan Map Domain: HexLocation, Resource type, and the value of chit
    IPort
    Represents the port in a Catan game Domain: Resource type, Hex location, the trade ratio
